law.catch_line: No person may sell, pack, offer, or expose for sale, or ship into the State for these purposes, any ...
law.text: No person may sell, pack, offer, or expose for sale, or ship into the State for these purposes, any Irish potatoes or parts of them intended for propagation purposes, which do not conform to the standards of certified Irish potatoes and U.S. No. 1 Irish potatoes as provided in this subtitle.
